          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals189"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Rage (Ex):</strong></span> A <a href="ch73s48.html#MonstersAnimals187">wolverine</a> that takes damage in combat flies into a berserk rage on its next turn, clawing and biting madly until either it or its opponent is dead. It gains +4 to Strength, +4 to Constitution, and -2 to Armor Class. The creature cannot end its rage voluntarily.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2326866"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersAnimals190"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> <a href="ch73s48.html#MonstersAnimals187">Wolverines</a> have a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks and can always choose to take 10 on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks, even if rushed or threatened.</p>
